♪ THROUGH THESE SKIES ON HIGH ♪

379
00:22:44,666 --> 00:22:47,458
♪ WITH OUR GOAL IN SIGHT ♪

380
00:22:47,541 --> 00:22:50,208
♪ WE WILL RUN
