00:23:17,958 --> 00:23:20,083
- Yasunobu: WHAT? YOU'RE
JOINING THE TRACK TEAM?

391
00:23:20,166 --> 00:23:22,833
- Yamato: THAT'S RIGHT. I NEED
TO GET CLOSER TO ASAHINA,

392
00:23:22,916 --> 00:23:24,958
AND I FIGURED,
THIS IS MY LAST CHANCE.

393
00:23:25,041 --> 00:23:28,083
I HAVE TO MAKE IT WORK.
I CAN'T STAND TO LOSE HER.

394
00:23:28,166 --> 00:23:29,583
- Yasunobu: I HOPE YOU KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

395
00:23:29,666 --> 00:23:31,333
I DON'T WANNA SEE YOU
GET HURT AGAIN.

